679
00:48:05,219 --> 00:48:06,219
[SPEAKER_21]: What was their permit request?

680
00:48:06,239 --> 00:48:08,460
[SPEAKER_21]: Like when did their season technically start?

681
00:48:13,400 --> 00:48:13,700
[SPEAKER_06]: April.

682
00:48:17,183 --> 00:48:23,887
[SPEAKER_21]: I mean, they could potentially come to us next month, they might not be here now because they don't need it yet.

683
00:48:25,088 --> 00:48:27,510
[SPEAKER_21]: Well, I just think we get there.

684
00:48:28,691 --> 00:48:30,732
[SPEAKER_16]: So they were looking at Wednesdays and Thursdays.

685
00:48:30,812 --> 00:48:36,116
[SPEAKER_16]: And so what we can do is we can possibly just give them Mondays and Wednesdays or something to that effect.

686
